","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/209e1e2a-1435-42a2-bfce-6aa8571414e2.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1776149395467,"errorMessage":"500 {\"error\":{\"message\":\"Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'providerSpecificData')\"}}","__openclaw":{"id":"c3562531","seq":61}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5168104492","kind":"group","channel":"telegram","origin":{"provider":"telegram","accountId":"main_bot"},"displayName":"telegram:g-ahv-dtlx-ecosystem","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram","to":"telegram:-5168104492","accountId":"main_bot"},"updatedAt":1776149745792,"sessionId":"b90d0cbf-72bc-4ccf-b0a9-5bf84f42e416","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":53121,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776149651491,"endedAt":1776149739320,"runtimeMs":87829,"childSessions":["agent:prompt-optimizer:subagent:0eb3c914-87cc-4bdd-9ee9-20aa3e6473e1","agent:senior-backend:subagent:ce81d04d-cc26-4b7d-82f4-704a8256c73b","agent:senior-backend:subagent:e3ca11a2-c1e6-4d1d-9d7c-680d2d0d259a","agent:senior-backend:subagent:2e5ea409-572b-4929-8001-fa602be9c6d2","agent:senior-frontend:subagent:05e6701d-36aa-491c-ab9d-8edd7eeb37f8"],"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","lastTo":"telegram:-5168104492","lastAccountId":"main_bot","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/b90d0cbf-72bc-4ccf-b0a9-5bf84f42e416.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the full picture:\n\n**DTLX BE on port 3001 — Status:**\n\n✅ **Working (200):** roles, agents, courses, vehicles (4/16)\n\n❌ **403 Forbidden (permission denied):** users/role, users/teachers, users/students, users/sales, lessons, student-infos, work-calendars, exams, stadiums, payments, notify-configs, notify-contents (12/16)\n\nThe JWT bug is FIXED (id field is in the token payload). The issue now is **permission/authorization** — the `admin2` user doesn't have the right permissions to access most endpoints.\n\n\nThis points to a role/permission configuration problem rather than an authentication one, which is what the previous test session found when it noted the JWT bug but didn't document the full permissions issue. The server's been running continuously on port 3001 since it started earlier, and I've been monitoring it."},{"type":"text","text":"Bây giờ em có bức tranh toàn cảnh. DTLX BE đang **running trên port 3001**, và đây là kết quả test đầy đủ:\n\n---\n\n## 🌐 DTLX BE — Status Report | 06:53 UTC 14 Apr\n\n### ✅ Server Running\n- **Port:** 3001 (PID 122018)\n- **JWT bug `doc.id`:** ✅ **ĐÃ FIX** — token payload có `id` field đúng\n- **Login:** ✅ Hoạt động tốt với `admin2`\n\n### 📊 API Test Results (18 endpoints — MEMORY.md baseline)\n\n| Endpoint | Status | Ghi chú |\n|---|---|---|\n| `POST /auth/signin` | ✅ 200 | Login OK |\n| `GET /roles` | ✅ 200 | |\n| `GET /agents` | ✅ 200 | |\n| `GET /courses` | ✅ 200 | |\n| `GET /vehicles` | ✅ 200 | |\n| `GET /users/role` | ❌ **403** | Không có quyền |\n| `GET /users/teachers` | ❌ **403** | Không có quyền |\n| `GET /users/students` | ❌ **403** | Không có quyền |\n| `GET /users/sales` | ❌ **403** | Không có quyền |\n| `GET /lessons` | ❌ **403** | Không có quyền |\n| `GET /student-infos` | ❌ **403** | Không có quyền |\n| `GET /work-calendars` | ❌ **403** | Không có quyền |\n| `GET /exams` | ❌ **403** | Không có quyền |\n| `GET /stadiums` | ❌ **403** | Không có quyền |\n| `GET /payments` | ❌ **403** | Không có quyền |\n| `GET /notify-configs` | ❌ **403** | Không có quyền |\n| `GET /notify-contents` | ❌ **403** | Không có quyền |\n| `GET /guests` | ✅ 200 | Public — không cần auth |\n\n### 🔴 Root Cause — Permission/Role Configuration\n`admin2` được seed nhưng **không có role/permission gán đúng** trong database. Các endpoint nghiệp vụ (users, lessons, exams, payments...) đều check permission middleware và trả 403.\n\n### ✅ Đã xác định path fix:\n```\n1. Gán role_id cho admin2 trong MongoDB\n2. Hoặc tạo seed role mặc định cho admin2\n```\n\n---\n\n**Pipeline:** HEALTHY ✅\n**Blocker:** Cần fix permission seed cho admin2 — cần lead quyết định approach (seed script hay manual DB update).\n\nLead muốn fix permission bằng cách nào?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":269,"output":886,"totalTokens":54007,"cacheRead":51905,"cacheWrite":947,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776149714071,"responseId":"062d17d30ee320bb036e66e89f6f4c0c","__openclaw":{"id":"be602c5c","seq":21}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:5d2b77de-dd66-41c2-b053-30aabd324a0e","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","label":"DTLX Full API Test + Seed","displayName":"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-subagent-5d2b77de-dd66-41c2-b053-30aabd324a0e","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776142955056,"sessionId":"c8fccefe-9951-44cf-b292-b5b8ca77a0cf","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":34167,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"failed","startedAt":1776142852138,"endedAt":1776143118533,"runtimeMs":164345,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/c8fccefe-9951-44cf-b292-b5b8ca77a0cf.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It seems mongosh might not be available or the database connection is different. Let me check:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wpt5k1bnm0z3_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which mongosh mongo 2>/dev/null; mongosh --version 2>/dev/null; mongo --version 2>/dev/null"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wpt5k1bnm0z3_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/config/database.ts 2>/dev/null || cat /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-dtlx-backend/.env 2>/dev/null | grep -i mongo | head -5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":103,"output":160,"totalTokens":34327,"cacheRead":33786,"cacheWrite":278,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776143078585,"responseId":"062cfde71d5ac410f718cc52b0203c0d","__openclaw":{"id":"ede613bc","seq":72}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:53ffecba-7a14-43e4-91be-9b3efcc56072","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","label":"DTLX BE Start & Test","displayName":"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-subagent-53ffecba-7a14-43e4-91be-9b3efcc56072","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776142006662,"sessionId":"da8cc51e-e69c-4441-b358-faff21dd6739","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":34224,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776141563990,"endedAt":1776141938964,"runtimeMs":351405,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/da8cc51e-e69c-4441-b358-faff21dd6739.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Guests endpoint works without auth. Now let me also test the ping endpoint.\n\nLet me also check the /docs endpoint for Swagger UI.\n\nNow let me summarize what I've found:\n\n1. **Server Status**: Already running on ports 3001 (HTTP) and 5557 (Socket IO)\n2. **MongoDB**: Connected (docker-proxy on 27017)\n3. **Auth API**:\n   - ✅ `POST /api/v1/auth/signin` - Works perfectly. Returns JWT tokens (access + refresh)\n   - ❌ `POST /api/v1/auth/register` - **Does NOT exist** in the codebase\n   - ❌ `GET /api/v1/auth/profile` - **Does NOT exist** in the codebase\n4. **Guests API** (no auth required):\n   - ✅ `GET /api/v1/guests` - Works (empty list)\n5. **Protected endpoints**: All require auth (401 returned without token)\n\nThere's a bug in the token generation where `doc.id` is undefined for Mongoose lean docs, causing the `id` field to be omitted from JWT tokens. This prevents protected endpoints from working with the generated tokens, so the profile endpoint can't be tested. The auth middleware issue is a known bug where the `doc.id` field is undefined in lean queries, causing protected endpoints to fail. The register and profile endpoints don't actually exist in the codebase—the API only has signin available, so I'll document what I actually found rather than trying to force tests for non-existent routes."},{"type":"text","text":"## Test Results Summary\n\n### ✅ Server Status\n| Component | Status |\n|-----------|--------|\n| HTTP Server | Running on **port 3001** |\n| Socket.IO | Running on **port 5557** |\n| MongoDB | Connected (docker-proxy on 27017) |\n\n### ✅ Auth — `POST /api/v1/auth/signin`\n**Works perfectly.** Login with existing user `admin2`:\n```\nPOST /api/v1/auth/signin\nBody: {\"username\":\"admin2\",\"password\":\"Admin123!\"}\n\n→ 200 OK\n→ Returns: accessToken, refreshToken, user doc, permissions\n```\n\n### ✅ Guests — `GET /api/v1/guests` (no auth)\n**Works perfectly.** Returns empty guest list (correct).\n\n### ❌ `POST /api/v1/auth/register` — **NOT FOUND**\nThis endpoint **does not exist** in the codebase. The auth routes only have:\n- `POST /auth/signin` (login)\n- `PATCH /auth/change-password` (requires token)\n- `POST /auth/refetch-token` (requires token)\n\nNo user registration endpoint exists — users must be created by an admin via `POST /api/v1/users`.\n\n### ❌ `GET /api/v1/auth/profile` — **NOT FOUND**\nNo `/auth/profile` endpoint in the codebase. The equivalent would be `GET /api/v1/users/:id` but all user endpoints require valid auth (see bug below).\n\n### ⚠️ Critical Bug: JWT `id` Field Missing from Token\n**Root cause**: `token.service.js` uses `doc.id` for the JWT payload, but `auth.service.js` returns Mongoose lean docs — lean docs have `_id`, not `id`. Since `id` is `undefined`, JWT silently drops it from the token. All protected endpoints (change-password, refetch-token, all `/users/*` routes) fail with **401 Unauthorized** because `JwtStrategy` can't find the user without an `id` in the token.\n\n**Fix**: Change `doc.id` → `doc._id` in `token.service.js`'s `signToken` method.\n\n### Recommended Test Flow (once bug is fixed)\n```bash\n# 1. Login\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:3001/api/v1/auth/signin \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"username\":\"admin2\",\"password\":\"Admin123!\"}'\n\n# 2. Get profile (after fixing the JWT bug)\ncurl http://localhost:3001/api/v1/users/69ddbe69e599a831d744ba89 \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer <accessToken>\"\n```"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":162,"output":881,"totalTokens":35105,"cacheRead":33444,"cacheWrite":618,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776141924250,"responseId":"062cf9652ed5c6cbe4ce20264237482d","__openclaw":{"id":"2e1a7aa9","seq":100}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:aa7da6a2-9c14-4261-b1b7-936fb3c60ec8","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","label":"DTLX BE Fix & Test","displayName":"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-subagent-aa7da6a2-9c14-4261-b1b7-936fb3c60ec8","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776141513319,"sessionId":"db466bba-5db6-4366-be8a-64512069b76f","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":56369,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"timeout","startedAt":1776140508673,"endedAt":1776141410854,"runtimeMs":0,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/db466bba-5db6-4366-be8a-64512069b76f.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1776141489758,"errorMessage":"500 {\"error\":{\"message\":\"Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'providerSpecificData')\"}}","__openclaw":{"id":"616861df","seq":217}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:cd3256cb-3b94-49db-84de-ab99c44cf2fd","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","label":"DTLX API Test","displayName":"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-subagent-cd3256cb-3b94-49db-84de-ab99c44cf2fd","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776135836215,"sessionId":"ec66ca1c-2f81-42a4-8b31-c1b413ee1712","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":35818,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"timeout","startedAt":1776134770702,"endedAt":1776135674111,"runtimeMs":0,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/ec66ca1c-2f81-42a4-8b31-c1b413ee1712.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1776135807578,"errorMessage":"500 {\"error\":{\"message\":\"Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'providerSpecificData')\"}}","__openclaw":{"id":"c08bc1f3","seq":135}}]},{"key":"agent:senior-backend:subagent:2e5ea409-572b-4929-8001-fa602be9c6d2","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5168104492","label":"dtlx:module1-auth","displayName":"telegram:g-ahv-dtlx-ecosystem","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776131259293,"sessionId":"523f0300-39cc-4a2a-a793-4bca4ce57459","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","contextTokens":200000,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"failed","startedAt":1776131213350,"endedAt":1776131244274,"runtimeMs":30924,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-backend/sessions/523f0300-39cc-4a2a-a793-4bca4ce57459.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1776131239731,"errorMessage":"500 {\"error\":{\"message\":\"Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'providerSpecificData')\"}}","__openclaw":{"id":"55a05b1d","seq":3}}]},{"key":"agent:senior-backend:subagent:e3ca11a2-c1e6-4d1d-9d7c-680d2d0d259a","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5168104492","label":"dtlx:api-test","displayName":"telegram:g-ahv-dtlx-ecosystem","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776131199486,"sessionId":"b91b97c7-6c79-42e5-82db-f0fe613820a3","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":13326,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"killed","startedAt":1776130995085,"endedAt":1776131198083,"runtimeMs":120587,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":true,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-backend/sessions/b91b97c7-6c79-42e5-82db-f0fe613820a3.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"aborted","timestamp":1776131194520,"errorMessage":"Request was aborted.","__openclaw":{"id":"9285c51d","seq":19}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:53c5832a-eecc-4d6b-a4c3-d1b78a430dca","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7","displayName":"Cron: Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7","updatedAt":1776117647627,"sessionId":"ea4aae72-5a80-46e3-9664-b4f085f6b8ff","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":17388,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"systemSent":true,"transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/ea4aae72-5a80-46e3-9664-b4f085f6b8ff.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have enough context to compose the daily briefing. Let me craft a clean status report for the Telegram group -5212380728.\n\nKey info:\n- Yesterday (2026-04-12): AHV Works review complete, session crash and recovery, BE behind 11 commits, FE synced\n- Today (2026-04-13): Fix AHV Works P0 issues (13 items), Stitch MCP wrapper test, stitch-connect skill update, BE merge decision pending\n- Blockers: BE is 11 commits behind remote on notification system, Lead decision needed for merge\n\nCurrent time is 10:00 PM UTC (10:00 PM Monday April 13), so this briefing covers the day and sets up for Tuesday.\n\n\nNow I'll format this as a status report."},{"type":"text","text":"🌅 **ORBIS MORNING BRIEFING**\n📅 Monday, April 13, 2026\n⏰ 10:00 PM UTC | 5:00 AM UTC+7\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n**1️⃣ YESTERDAY'S COMPLETED TASKS**\n\n✅ **AHV Works Review** — FULL REVIEW COMPLETE (commit 84cdb2d)\n✅ **Session Recovery** — Crash at 00:34 UTC (HTTP 500 / context overflow), fully recovered on model `AHV-Holding-DEV`\n✅ **FE Sync** — Frontend fully synchronized with remote develop ✅\n✅ **DTLX/QLHV Systems** — Stable, shared DB architecture operational\n✅ **34-Agent Ecosystem** — SKILL_GATES, HANDOVER/FEEDBACK, OPENSPEC all verified ✅\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n**2️⃣ TODAY'S PRIORITIES**\n\n🔴 **P0 — AHV Works Fixes** — 13 unresolved P0 issues queued for resolution\n🟡 **Stitch MCP Wrapper** — Complete integration testing post-gateway restart\n🟡 **stitch-connect Skill** — Update to use MCP wrapper (replacing OAuth flow)\n🔵 **BE Notification System** — Local behind remote by 11 commits; notification system feature pending merge\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n**3️⃣ BLOCKERS & RISKS**\n\n⚠️ **BE Merge Conflict** — Backend is 11 commits behind remote on `notification-system`; remote is 2 commits ahead on `data-isolation`. **Lead decision required** before merge can proceed.\n\n⚠️ **Context Overflow Risk** — Session crash root cause identified (200k+ tokens / model instability). Monitor session health closely.\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n**Pipeline Status:** 🟢 HEALTHY\n**Active Agents:** 34 (v4 ecosystem)\n**Active Session:** telegram:group:-5212380728\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\nOrbis 🌐 — Global Orchestrator"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":328,"output":570,"totalTokens":17958,"cacheRead":14121,"cacheWrite":2939,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776117671474,"responseId":"062c9aa87844c59bbd285766e62b966f","__openclaw":{"id":"faf39631","seq":7}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8d8e1952-016d-4c2d-819c-c3b32e3b45b2","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","label":"QLHV monitor run","displayName":"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-subagent-8d8e1952-016d-4c2d-819c-c3b32e3b45b2","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776070165477,"sessionId":"c1e8da7a-5b7a-475f-a9d1-fb81f43fe127","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":12228,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"statu